I've been looking at an existing Documentum web application. No tests exist.
As part of maintaining the app I've been wanting to create JUnit test cases
to document current behaviour prior to making changes. Unfortunately the
Documentum object model is so integral to practically everything that I
haven't been able to create tests for anything substantial.

Has anyone had previous experience with testing this product?

Michael Rutherfurd
